Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"When Zeus spoke, all the tribes of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,who live on the face of the Earth\Nlearned to sow and reap the fields."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl, your pronunciation is off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm trying my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've improved a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "This is\None heck of an awful student."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-How is he now?\N-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That Japanese physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he travels around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to meet\Nthat man again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a job? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of job is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an interior coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must have\None heck of an eye for good furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My work isn't quite the same\Nas what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It must seem ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,considering I've hardly spent\Neven a minute in a kitchen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll have you do my kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet any kitchen\Nyou design will cost a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not drinking, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Not a drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take things nice and gradual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush. Just like always,\Ntoday will end and tomorrow will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's what happiness is."\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick of hearing that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that just knowing I was\Nwaiting at the station made him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,People are so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sadness fades away quickly,\Nwhile only our happy memories remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,People are designed to have\Nsuch convenient memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we're able to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Verdemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the lawyer who cleared\Nthe charges against you, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out as much about you\Nas I possibly could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a product of Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As an intelligence agent for East Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you played the role of a journalist\Nand traveled the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You later investigated human rights\Nissues as a freelance journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You would carry an enormous bag
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,packed with mounds of documents\Nto back up your findings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But one thing I was never\Nable to discover was your true name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wolfgang Grimmer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He left us without telling us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an inspector anymore,\NDetective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you became a professor\Nat the police university.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've been able to talk\Nto my daughter a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though that's not accurate.\NWe communicate by email.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, my daughter and I lived\Nour lives without ever speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew nothing about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,just how much\Nare we able to truly communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have had a lot\Nyou wanted to tell us…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,over a nice beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're returning to Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The company I'm working for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That place has a lot of memories--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Running from things is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is dealing with the truth\Nand getting on with life."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get rid of this if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen and I can help\Nwhenever you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter and him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Send them my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Questioning of Dr. Tenma continues."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"The full story of the incident\Nis still unclear."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Testimony by Inspector Lunge begins."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Will this be Europe's\Nmost horrific mass murder?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma was completely exonerated.'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"The police department indicates\Nit will issue an apology to Dr. Tenma."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"The motive for the murders\Nis still unclear."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is the young man\Nwho is the real murderer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"The University of Münster Medical School\Ninvites Dr. Tenma to be professor."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma still firmly declines."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dr. Tenma joins Doctors Without Borders."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The articles just get shorter and shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,People are designed to have\Nconvenient memories, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure grown up since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Heckel, you've surely become\Na lot sleazier since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've still got quite a mouth on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I have soccer practice.\NI can't chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Tenma come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! He goes and joins\NDoctors Without Borders
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so he looks cool doing stuff\Nthat doesn't make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get ahold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if he comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me some work a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But considering the cost and labor,\Nhe didn't pay me nearly enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma gave you work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was a simple search for\Nsomeone, but it was a huge inconvenience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to steal police secrets.\NWhat if I'd been caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Tenma this bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can't pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,tell him I'll make him do\Nunderground doctor work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,SOUTHERN FRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't visited in such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I went abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please share these with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Such lovely weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All the leaves are photosynthesized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Life… Infinite numbers of genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about Mendel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He developed\Nthe genetic inheritance theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I attended the same university\Nthat Mendel did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The University of Brno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a city in Moravia\Nin the southeastern Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lovely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to visit it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming here so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoy the time I spend with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a very good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling\Nthat I can tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how frightening it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,questions for me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the mother of twins, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was part of his experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the children growing inside me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear they will take vengeance on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't… let go of my hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is… the real monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children are alive, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembered what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not ever remember again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd better say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave those children names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Their names are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Still maintaining\Nyour reputation for tardiness, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ten minutes late\Nfor your appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Professor Kronecker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know\Nwhy I asked you to come here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about your graduation thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been quite difficult for you\Nto make up for your time off from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no excuse for bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, your thesis was…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,best in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the students I have taught,\Nthis is the finest thesis I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that you can help many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You may go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,tardiness in court may earn you contempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your thesis?\NIf you failed, you've still got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll have you comfort me\Nthe next time I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to fool me!\NI can tell by your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You passed, didn't you? Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's plenty of hard work to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate! Hurry home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get back that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got work\Nand a lot of plans with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NTenma's coming back, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He just called!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said he has to go abroad again soon\Nfor Doctors Without Borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll be back tomorrow.\NYou'd better get here fast, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, about tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't meet up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,BAVARIA STATE POLICE HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in a coma this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoke with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something\Nthat I only want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the monster came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your hands off my children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stay away from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave one with you\Nand take one with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So which one shall we take away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, don't let go of…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my mother try to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did she mix me up with my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us didn't she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by: Brian Athey
